<link wikidata="" start="21154" end="21240" title="Farmers and Fishermen: Two Centuries of Work in Essex County, Massachusetts, 1630–1850" label="Farmers and Fishermen: Two Centuries of Work in Essex County, Massachusetts, 1630–1850"/>
